This is just a simple README file used to test github for my first public project.

files:

hello2.cpp  (C++ helloworld code)
hello.c     (C hello world code)
hellolib.c  (C hello world "library" code)
makefile    (makefile used to build the executables)

actions:

make       (defaults to "all")
make all   (builds C and C++ code and then runs both)

extras:

./hello  This stuff has extra args 

e.g.:

        Hello C World !!! 

        Hellolib: argc: 6
        Hellolib: This[1]
        Hellolib: stuff[2]
        Hellolib: has[3]
        Hellolib: extra[4]
        Hellolib: args[5]

